{"tid":2462523,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇返工兄弟好驚屙緊屎嗰陣會收到上司同事電話？","createTime":"2021-03-26T05:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T10:36:35.000Z","uid":40930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"13a7a40d43f5fcebb364556b44c8c8ed244ec57d","tid":2462523,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"返工屙屎例排都係上下連登打下機<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係有時無啦啦手機震一震見到上司同事call你就驚撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔接又唔係，接咗好驚佢會聽到我屙屎，就算唔係你屙隔離鄰居都可能突然「咚」一聲屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果成件事就好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又會驚突然屎意來潮，講講下突然呀一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對面就會問你發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：為己為人，同事去咗屙屎就唔好打電話煩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6290486c479957122f1393844922c873236b26b6","tid":2462523,"uid":73275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"唔撚接 做緊大事點接<br />\n做完大事先問佢咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714cc64dd587fce098d2bdc429b0a33c33651658","tid":2462523,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"照聽 收音唔會收到"},{"pid":"c8efa44a9b25a37c94ab3abc8c5c1a0550a82b98","tid":2462523,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"沖涼打黎都週不時啦😂"},{"pid":"472c35477a95b384a3d6b61cb5a013f1c87d8241","tid":2462523,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8efa44a9b25a37c94ab3abc8c5c1a0550a82b98","tid":2462523,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"沖涼打黎都週不時啦😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"facetime<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a88e0b0207769e53a815daa91106cbac4dfab2f","tid":2462523,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"喺香港返工識控制壓水花係基本吧<br />\n叫黎生教吓你"},{"pid":"a443076a71dfe19316a6ed3c2717b91af04a44b8","tid":2462523,"uid":64257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"大大聲講辦大事 收埋佢線"},{"pid":"673ccb067c9c7e71db4876d49dba639d9ab069db","tid":2462523,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:31:29.000Z","msg":"唔聽<br />\n一陣覆佢"},{"pid":"e214bf2ad469f075caaf86c40f71188a724fa2f9","tid":2462523,"uid":45985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"屙比佢聽"},{"pid":"c4e7c2f8ce0b13877c91a7898377b159ad783be0","tid":2462523,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"諗起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外,我有一段時間好鐘意入女廁痾屎事先聲明，我唔係變態佬，我唔會執佢地用過d m巾黎聞，亦都唔會響入面打飛機我入去真係為左痾屎，不過我既痾法有小小特別我入到去唔會即刻痾，我會等有人入黎先開始痾聽到有人入黎之後，我會好用力咁爆d屎出黎唔知點解，我好鐘意俾人聽到我放屁痾屎既聲，一諗起佢地聽到我屎眼發出既聲音，我就會痾得好舒暢 再講多次，我唔係變態，我只係鐘意痾屎俾人聽，就好似有d人鐘意唱歌俾人聽一樣不過我已經好耐無入女廁，因為驚俾人捉到以為我係變態佬依家我痾屎既時候會求其打個電話，然後痾俾電話入面既人聽如果你接過d電話，一聽就砵砵聲既話，好有可能係我打黎"}]}